Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她跟豪豪分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豪豪就是有办法找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打电话给她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}反反覆覆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}象咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}象催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她逃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}存款里还有50万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}50万花完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这都是10年前的事情了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是2001年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全世界都在迎接新世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}庆祝千禧年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看的懂这个简体字没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"证书"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我参加魔术比赛得到的一个证书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}写英文 你要翻译一下才看的懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我翻译一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在大陆比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么大陆要写英文？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为这样感觉上比较专业一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它的意思就是 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}丁建中 啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}参加这次世界魔术比赛得到了铜奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的表演的名和叫梦幻飞鸽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么飞 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5000块奖金哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}台市2币2万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5000块奖金在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把它变出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}信封里面是空的 我已经花完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我这次参加的是世界比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以回来之后用的都是国际的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在不用中国 也不用台湾的硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我用美金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}完全是崇洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}各位看看我这里有几枚硬币？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}几枚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5个硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}左手边几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我袖子是举高的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这边2个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}右手几个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 3个 - 确定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1个 2个 3个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 几个？- 3个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我握住之后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再做一次哦 1个 2个 3个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}4个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5个 握住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1个 2个 3个 4个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky 你手借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}握住 靠在这个桌子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}总共有几个硬币？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}4个 我这还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}5个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}掌户鼓励一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要喷 很可怕的 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看你怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雷大雨小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生日快乐 金妮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在干嘛？这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好失败的道具哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是我特别从大陆带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这么大一支只有一条而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}传过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要不要大杯一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不用了 我够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最大杯的给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最大杯的给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有谁没有？还有谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都有了吗？够不够杯子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了吗？好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把腿打开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她16岁就出来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟萱萱几乎每个礼拜六
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都会从基隆坐火车到台北
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在火车的厕所里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她们一起呼饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把自己HIGH到某种境界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她跟小豪认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是在和平东路的一个DISCO PUB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Spin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那一天她跟萱萱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约了朋友一起去唱卡拉0K
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}结果被放鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪他们一群人就走进来搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约他们一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪一整个晚上都盯看她看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一点沉默 害羞 - 看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她高中并没有毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他不让她参加毕业考试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在考试前的一个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们住在一个宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他故意不叫醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他不要她去考试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他不要她离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们想住在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在台北租了个房子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可他们都没有做事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有时候为了一千块坐车回基隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟他的同学借
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他偷了他爸爸的劳力士表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当了8万块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被他爸爸友现了 打电话来问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他死都不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他爸爸就报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那天风很大 阳光很亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}警察来了 查到了当票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们被带去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}隔壁桌的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是很熟 见进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 他是谁啊？- 豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不太熟 怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他干嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你认识她呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}认识呀 怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他可能要把Vicky吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要把Vicky呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他妈的 你怎祥？走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他妈的 打我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事 隔壁桌的 喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进来 进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放开手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了啦 不要这样子 不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你自己放忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没拿就是没拿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我爸爸打的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他说你拿的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 干嘛？- 热水器坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 热水器坏了？- 没有热水了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不热了封不封？- NO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你先把冷水关掉 只开热水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 热水开了吗？- 开了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有 还是冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你有全开？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可能没电了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我去买电池 - 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 快回来哦 - 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 帮我开门哦 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么那么慢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好 刑事组
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请问段钧豪先生是不是住在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.96,0:24:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有什么事事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为段钧豪有一些案子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们拿检查官的搜索票
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.36,0:24:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我们来查看一下 他在不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.04,0:24:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他不在 他今天早上出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那我们是不是简单的做一下搜索动作？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.40,0:24:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为他的案子跟他有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.96,0:25:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是不是请你也在场？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你们要…- 对 他住哪个房间 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}段钧豪住哪个房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.92,0:25:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就这么大 他住那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.08,0:25:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他住那里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这间是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们稍微警戒一下 你跟我来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小姐 麻烦一下好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.80,0:25:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们简单做一个搜索 希望你在场
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为他的案子跟他有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.08,0:25:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就必须简单做一个搜索 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.96,0:25:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我要进去吗？- 进来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.76,0:25:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一般他的衣物在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.96,0:25:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 这里 - 所有都是的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我和他的放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.35,0:25:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他什么时候回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:25:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不知道 - 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.36,0:26:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们要搜什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.80,0:26:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们怀疑他跟一个盗窃案有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}盗窃案？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.96,0:26:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我们有搜索票
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.88,0:26:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你就是段钧豪先生？- 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-是不是？- 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:26:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一桩盗窃案跟你有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.50,0:26:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们有检查官的搜索票
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.80,0:26:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}给你看一下我的证件
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.88,0:27:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们是重案组的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.84,0:27:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你先在那边坐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.96,0:27:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请跟我们来一下你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}段先生 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.96,0:27:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪为了不去当兵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.16,0:27:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把自己弄的很瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.76,0:27:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安非他命抽的很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.88,0:27:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪常常偷偷检查她的皮包
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.16,0:27:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}发下没有地址的发票
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.28,0:27:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他会打电话去问
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.80,0:27:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说要补盖店章
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.16,0:27:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪常为了她电话卡上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.44,0:27:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}的一通很长的电话孔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.28,0:27:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}责问她
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}用热水瓶丢她
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.16,0:27:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她收衣服要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.92,0:27:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他又哭看求她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪常常会写一些纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.92,0:28:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.76,0:28:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们属于不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他说你是从你的世界掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.36,0:28:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}掉到我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.72,0:28:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以你不懂我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你抽的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.36,0:30:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.88,0:30:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛不给我抽？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.80,0:30:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你懂什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.03,0:30:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你懂什么？你抽什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}给我啊 要抽大家一起抽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.36,0:30:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要抽大家一起抽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.32,0:31:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你抽啊 你抽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.80,0:31:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.40,0:31:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.96,0:31:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干什么啊 你？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.80,0:31:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你给我丢掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.76,0:31:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}给我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.84,0:31:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叫你吸毒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.44,0:33:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么这个电话打这么久？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.96,0:33:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我打回家啊 - 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.08,0:33:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打回基隆啊 长途
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.16,0:33:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打回家怎么不用家里的电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.88,0:33:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会用电话卡打？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.04,0:33:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我刚好在外面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.12,0:33:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你他妈的又在耍我了 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.04,0:33:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我耍你干嘛啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.35,0:34:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你干嘛要翻我东西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.44,0:34:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.38,0:34:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打回家
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.32,0:34:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.40,0:34:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我告诉你我是打回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.96,0:34:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 到底是谁？- 你不讲道理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.72,0:34:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你发疯啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.80,0:34:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你到底是打给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.76,0:34:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我说过我打回基隆家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.40,0:34:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有病啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我跟你讲 你最好别骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.36,0:34:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}神经病 我骗你干嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.05,0:34:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我他妈的会扁你 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}妈的 你有事没事搜我东西干嘛啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.88,0:34:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么祥？就是要搜 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.76,0:34:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你神经病啊你 - 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}变态
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.92,0:35:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说谁变态？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.04,0:35:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说谁变态？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.36,0:35:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说谁啊？到底打给谁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.88,0:35:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}讲话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我告诉你了 可你不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.21,0:35:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那我还能说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.36,0:36:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.08,0:36:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.08,0:36:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.08,0:36:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你干嘛？- 你走开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.04,0:36:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走了就不要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.36,0:36:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}妈的 谁要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.04,0:36:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.96,0:36:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}付不出房租
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.84,0:36:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}房东介绍她去制服店上班
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.32,0:36:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每天从家里到公司
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.96,0:37:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}上班中间 下班之前
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.72,0:37:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豪豪都会打电话来盯她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.04,0:37:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她晚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他会蹲在楼梯门□等她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.88,0:37:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他妒忌她有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.72,0:37:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可是他从来不工作
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.96,0:37:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他常常带一堆朋友来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.16,0:37:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.36,0:37:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}克药
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.84,0:37:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打电动
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.12,0:37:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}音乐开的很大声
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.08,0:37:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她在制服店上班的时候 遇见捷哥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.80,0:38:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们以前在Spin就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.08,0:38:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥常常送她回基隆
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.96,0:38:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喜欢带看她到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.96,0:38:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥身边永远有一堆人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.84,0:38:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一堆麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.80,0:38:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥从来不拒绝任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.12,0:38:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所有人都找捷哥讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.28,0:38:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谈事情
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.08,0:38:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她知道捷哥是纵容她的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.88,0:38:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么场合都带看她
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.96,0:38:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他带她
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.44,0:38:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有时候就象带看小兄弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.12,0:40:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 再一杯 - 在干嘛啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.72,0:41:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们全家人都住在台湾吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.28,0:41:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有 现在有
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.96,0:41:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爸爸这边的在台湾的还有阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.76,0:41:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一些住在日本北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.16,0:41:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 在日本？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.84,0:41:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去过那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.88,0:41:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没去过北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.84,0:41:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很冷很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.36,0:41:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们什么时候回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.28,0:41:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后天
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.84,0:41:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我可以去找你们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.28,0:42:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我去日本的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.32,0:42:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}自然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.76,0:42:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}电话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.20,0:42:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她认识竹内康竹内淳两兄弟的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.96,0:42:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是在Texound 的DISCO PUB
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们让她想起豪豪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}沉默 害羞…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们的父亲是台湾人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.96,0:42:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}母亲是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.76,0:42:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们在北海道的夕张出生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.96,0:42:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个煤矿山城
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.92,0:42:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在煤矿已经关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.16,0:42:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}改成了博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.96,0:42:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夕张还住看他们的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.96,0:42:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开了一家很老的居酒屋
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.84,0:43:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每年二月 夕张电影节的时候很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.96,0:43:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们的母亲要他们回来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.04,0:43:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竹内康说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.20,0:43:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夕张电影节的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.76,0:43:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们每天都忙到夜里两三点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.08,0:43:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}居酒屋满满的都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.92,0:43:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他说夕张有一条电影街
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.40,0:43:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两边的商店都挂看电影的看牌
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.04,0:43:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都是很老的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.84,0:43:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有寅次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.96,0:43:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}石原裕次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.96,0:43:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}卓别林
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.96,0:43:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竹内淳说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他外婆进80岁生日的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.92,0:43:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们全家都回夕张
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.96,0:43:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们跟外婆说
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.96,0:44:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}外婆要好好的活到90岁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.96,0:44:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但外婆说
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.32,0:44:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她想活到100岁
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.88,0:44:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她想看那今时候
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.76,0:44:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夕张会变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.84,0:50:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得 其实我们是两个不同世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.16,0:50:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道我们怎么会在同一个世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}神经病啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.36,0:51:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.40,0:51:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 听没听到我刚给你讲的？- 讲什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.28,0:52:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好好跟你讲 你也这么凶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.96,0:52:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟我在一起很痛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.80,0:53:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.96,0:54:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.32,0:54:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们继续玩
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.84,0:54:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我已经很投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}段钧豪
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.04,0:55:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 怎么了？- 帮看一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.84,0:57:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 脱下来 - 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.76,0:57:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想要怎么样嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.12,0:57:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.28,0:58:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.96,0:58:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}洗澡呀？一起洗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.96,0:58:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你走
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.44,0:59:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.04,0:59:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.80,0:59:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.16,0:59:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你拉不动我的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.76,0:59:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}马上出去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.44,0:59:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你进来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.04,0:59:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}手放开
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.80,0:59:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}手放开听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.72,0:59:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你神经病啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.84,1:00:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她跟豪豪分手了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.20,1:00:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豪豪就是有办法找到她
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.84,1:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打电话给她
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.44,1:00:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}求她回来
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.28,1:00:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}反反覆覆
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.96,1:00:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}象咒语
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.88,1:00:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}象催眠
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.96,1:01:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她逃不了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她又回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.96,1:01:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.84,1:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}存款里还有50万
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.28,1:01:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}50万花完了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.76,1:01:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就分手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.72,1:01:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.80,1:01:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你进来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.84,1:01:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有事跟你说
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.40,1:02:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到外面讲 好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.84,1:02:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 什么事情？- 没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.96,1:02:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们到外面讲
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.92,1:02:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.88,1:02:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪 干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.76,1:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可不可以？到外面讲好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.16,1:02:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有话就在这边讲嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.80,1:02:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到外面我有话跟你讲
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.96,1:02:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以吗？好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.76,1:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 怎么祥？- 我有事情跟她讲
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.84,1:03:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们聊一下 他们有事讲
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.96,1:03:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky 有没有问题？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.92,1:03:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Vicky没问题啦 - 我有事情和她说
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.76,1:03:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}修哥 Vicky没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.40,1:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪 没你的事 操
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.84,1:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事了 没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.96,1:03:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豆哥
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.08,1:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豆哥 没事 修哥 没事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.36,1:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们聊两句 一下就好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.40,1:03:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让他们讲一下 马上就好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.96,1:03:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你讲啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.96,1:03:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我到外面 这是我跟她的事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.28,1:03:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 什么叫你跟她的事？- 没事了 没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.88,1:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事吧 Vicky ？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.36,1:03:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么叫你跟她的事啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.85,1:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁不知道我跟她在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.16,1:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}老大 没事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.84,1:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}黄修 不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.28,1:04:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 修哥
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.96,1:04:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}手放开
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.96,1:04:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}修哥不要这样 他们聊一下而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.76,1:04:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你他妈的不要废话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.04,1:04:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.96,1:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}黄修 不要动
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.04,1:04:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky 你要不要跟我去？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.88,1:04:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你愿不愿意？方不方便？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.80,1:04:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我跟她的事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.14,1:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么叫你跟她的事？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.96,1:04:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.90,1:04:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们他妈不是人啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.80,1:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出去就好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.96,1:04:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 捷哥 状况我了解 真的是 - 好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.20,1:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.44,1:04:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她自己会处理
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.44,1:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 那我方不方便跟她讲句话？- 可以
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.96,1:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 可以吗？- Vicky 你自己处理
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.92,1:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay 问题HIGH了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.76,1:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么了 Vicky ？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.96,1:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来 先进来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.84,1:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把鞋脱了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.16,1:06:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪对你动手是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.76,1:06:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.92,1:07:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.96,1:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥 你有比较淡的烟吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.04,1:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有 只有这个烟了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.32,1:09:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有辣椒酱吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.12,1:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.80,1:10:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这可以开吗？这好象比较辣
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.84,1:11:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好了吗？- 这里
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.96,1:11:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我帮你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.04,1:11:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想先喝鱼酒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.80,1:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就3还是要少喝
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.40,1:12:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开胃
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.80,1:12:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宝利的毒还没戒掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.72,1:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很难嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.88,1:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宝利的妈妈听一个师傅讲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.96,1:12:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}希望多替她念经
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.76,1:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对她有一鱼帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.80,1:12:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样念有用吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.88,1:12:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我就答应她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.67,1:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每天替她念三次
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.88,1:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有用的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.96,1:12:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有看这她吗？她有比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.96,1:12:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还是这样？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.96,1:13:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你的烟
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.44,1:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要少喝鱼酒了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.32,1:14:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我妈刚来进
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.16,1:14:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.08,1:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我妈和我哥去小豪那边帮我拿衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.80,1:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们说
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.40,1:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小豪把我的衣服全都剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.88,1:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就只留一个手机给我 没坏
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.16,1:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那你跟小豪之间
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.32,1:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.44,1:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我跟他就这样子了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.32,1:15:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我在想
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.28,1:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我在想我现在应该
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.96,1:15:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不想
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.84,1:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不想回制服店上班
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.28,1:15:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也不晓得要干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.12,1:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我妈要我跟她一起回去基隆
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.12,1:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可我又不想回去
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.88,1:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也不晓得应该怎么亦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.16,1:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不回制服店上班…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.96,1:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也好啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.32,1:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那种坏境是非多
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.32,1:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}钱赚的多 你花的也快
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.08,1:16:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你现在最主要是要回归正常
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.84,1:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你看象我咖啡厅里的工读生打工
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.86,1:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一天80块而已
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.12,1:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个小时80块
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.32,1:16:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可是他们都很充实 很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.76,1:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就是所谓的正常
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.44,1:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有没有什么要我帮忙的？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.12,1:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想我现在可以去咖啡厅打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.44,1:16:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这也很好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.16,1:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.76,1:18:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.76,1:18:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们在石头场子里动手脚 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.80,1:19:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 电话来了- 谁？石头？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.80,1:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}找了个变魔术的 建中是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们怎么这样啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.20,1:19:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.88,1:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人家现在已经很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.20,1:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在要幼动作了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.44,1:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们怎么竟做这些麻烦事？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.80,1:19:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他怎么说嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.88,1:19:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他说会有一些麻烦 叫我看看处理
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.96,1:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看这个事情没那么好处理
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.96,1:20:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}陪我喝酒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.96,1:20:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豆子 豆子
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.28,1:20:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂？请说
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.08,1:20:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 知道
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.40,1:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事好不好？他怎么说嘛 捷哥？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.80,1:20:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在也不知道怎么处理了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.28,1:20:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}建中人呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.36,1:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}石头那边告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.80,1:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.96,1:21:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你先回去 好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.76,1:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们先送Vicky回去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.32,1:21:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Vicky 先回去了 - 没事哦？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.20,1:21:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky 先回去
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.12,1:21:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没矢系 我处理好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.96,1:21:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是你处理 我来做个联络
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.40,1:21:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是那么好处理的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.88,1:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我不要 - 听话 先回去休息
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.16,1:28:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他留下钥匙和手机给你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.80,1:29:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Vicky 是我
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.88,1:29:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在在日本
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.40,1:29:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为你睡的很熟 所以我没叫醒你
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.36,1:29:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豆子出事了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.76,1:29:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事情到现在还没解决
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.36,1:29:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我可能还要在日本呆上一阵子
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.44,1:29:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在住在新宿大久保车站附近的饭店甲隆阁
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.96,1:29:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}电话号码是33695526
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.28,1:29:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}33695526
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.04,1:29:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我住在403号房间
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.88,1:29:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}假如你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.92,1:30:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想出来散心 可以来日本找我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.76,1:30:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我来日本的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.94,1:30:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}千万不要告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.80,1:30:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.12,1:31:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喂 捷哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.28,1:31:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}高先生？你是谁？他不在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.96,1:34:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥一直没有出现
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.92,1:34:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也没有电话
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.80,1:34:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她记得东京那年下雪
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.80,1:34:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她带看捷哥留给她的电话四处游荡
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.20,1:34:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捷哥离开了她
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.96,1:34:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大街上都是行色匆匆的上班族 学生
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.32,1:34:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}家庭主妇
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.20,1:35:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她让自己象他们中的一份子
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.96,1:35:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吃拉面 看电视冠军
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.84,1:35:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}披看捷哥留下来的夹克
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.88,1:35:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有看香烟和古龙水混合的气味
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.76,1:35:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她知道捷哥是想念她的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.20,1:35:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才要她来日本
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.08,1:35:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他叫她不要告诉别人他在日本
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.20,1:35:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}意思就是说…你来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.96,1:35:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个人来
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.72,1:36:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夕张纪念之北海道
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.76,1:36:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竹内康说
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.16,1:36:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夕张的冬天很冷
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.96,1:36:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}零下三十几度
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.12,1:36:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她想那是雪人的故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.44,1:36:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雪人最后在太阳升起的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.40,1:36:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}融化不见了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.96,1:36:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一次她跟豪豪做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.80,1:36:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她忽然觉得
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.96,1:36:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}豪豪就象雪人一样
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.80,1:36:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在太阳升起的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.84,1:36:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}消失不见
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.76,1:37:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}非常悲伤的做爱这程
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.80,1:37:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使在多年以后
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.76,1:37:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她还记得
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.96,1:37:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这都是她十年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.96,1:37:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那时候是2001年
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.96,1:37:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那年
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.96,1:37:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那年夕张 大雪

